bilingual.source: The company repaid its debts ahead of schedule.
The company repaid its loans ahead of schedule.
We've finished the project ahead of schedule.
bilingual.target: 我们已经提前完成了项目。

bilingual.source: You advisably finished the task ahead of time.
bilingual.target: 你明智地提前完成了任务。

bilingual.source: The subordinate completed the task ahead of schedule.
The worker completed the task ahead of schedule.
bilingual.target: 这位工人提前完成了任务。

bilingual.source: The contractor completed the work ahead of schedule.
bilingual.target: 承包商提前完成了工作。

bilingual.source: Planning ahead can reduce the completion time.
bilingual.target: 提前计划可以缩短完成时间。

bilingual.source: The project was completely finished ahead of schedule.
bilingual.target: 项目完全地提前完成了。

bilingual.source: The team breezed through the project ahead of schedule.
bilingual.target: 团队提前轻松完成了项目。

list.abstract: AHEAD，英文单词，副词，翻译为在前、预先、领先等。

yingyinNormal.en: Has new material arrived ahead of schedule?
yingyinNormal.zh: 有新的资料提前到了吗

yingyinNormal.en: Good someone's read ahead. Remember that. You'll need that in 3 years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很好，看来提前看书了，记住，未来三年都要这么做。

yingyinNormal.en: Try it. Go ahead. It's good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你尝尝，吃吧。挺好吃的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, go on ahead. I'll catch up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们先走一步，我马上就来。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's see what you got. Go ahead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我们看看你拿到了什么。给他看吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, I'll go ahead and put "yes."
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我，我就选“是”了。

yingyinNormal.en: Go ahead. It'll be a piece of kelp.
yingyinNormal.zh: 去吧，你没问题的。

yingyinNormal.en: I know that look. What is it? Go ahead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这表情我见过，想什么呢，直说吧，

yingyinNormal.en: Go ahead. You're gonna be late. Go. Go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说吧。你要迟到了！快去。

yingyinNormal.en: No. I think he can handle it. Go ahead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我想他可以应付，回答吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Go ahead, panda. Show us what you can do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 来吧，熊猫，让我们见识一下你的本领。

yingyinNormal.en: Commander, I have an idea. Go ahead, Mark.
yingyinNormal.zh: 指挥官，我有个点子。说吧，马克。

yingyinNormal.en: Such as? Let's not get ahead of ourselves.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有什么结果？别得意忘形了。

yingyinNormal.en: Get them back to Stormwind. We ride ahead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你带他俩先回去暴风城，我们先走。

yingyinNormal.en: What? Doesn't matter. No, go ahead, say it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么? 算了说吧。没事，说啊！

yingyinNormal.en: Fine, go ahead. Trust me, we are not a couple.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，你说。拜托，我们才不是情侣。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, go ahead. Hi Annie. Fantastic! You got it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，请说吧，快说话，安妮，你好，太好了，你成功了！

yingyinNormal.en: No, go ahead. Blair, think we could meet tonight?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，走吧，布莱尔，今晚我们见个面怎么样?

yingyinNormal.en: Go ahead, kid. You gotta Farkle, you gotta Farkle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请自便，小子，要“放屁”就放吧。

yingyinNormal.en: You're right, sir. You have got a tricky day ahead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说的没错，长官，你今天麻烦事估计不少。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The performance was a creative call to action <highlight>ahead</highlight> of November's United Nations Climate Change Conference in Glasgow, UK.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这场演出是对11月在英国格拉斯哥举行的联合国气候变化会议的创造性呼吁。

examination_example.sentence: But with legal battles <highlight>ahead</highlight>, the zone's future looks uncertain at best.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但随着法律斗争的展开，该区的未来充其量只能说是不确定。

examination_example.sentence: Rather than pulling students back, a gap year pushes them <highlight>ahead</highlight> by preparing them for independence, new responsibilities and environmental changes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 间隔年不是让学生退缩，而是让他们为独立、新的责任和环境变化做好准备，从而推动他们前进。

sense_info_list.en: further forward in time; in advance; in the near future

examination_example.sentence: Imagining the outcome of following through on one's curiosity <highlight>ahead</highlight> of time can help determine whether it is worth the endeavor.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 提前想象一下跟随自己好奇心的结果有助于确定努力是否值得。

examination_example.sentence: Planning <highlight>ahead</highlight> should eliminate wastage.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 提前计划应该能消除浪费。

word_usage.usage:
ahead既可以表示在前面（指位置），如：
run ahead  向前跑  
ahead也可以表示向前（指方向），例如
the road ahead  前面的路

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Scotland will reach the national target in carbon emissions reduction <highlight>ahead</highlight> of schedule.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 苏格兰将提前实现碳减排的国家目标。

examination_example.sentence: They have announced a range of strategies in an attempt to reduce carbon emissions <highlight>ahead</highlight> of the new national target of 2045.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们宣布了一系列策略，试图在2045年新的国家目标之前减少碳排放。

examination_example.sentence: What did ScottishPower's chief executive say <highlight>ahead</highlight> of the All Energy Conference?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 苏格兰电力公司的首席执行官在全能源大会之前说了什么?

sense_info_list.en: further forward in time; in advance; in the near future

examination_example.sentence: Now, of course, we know that whatever you call it, human behavior is warming the planet, with grave consequences <highlight>ahead</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在，当然，我们知道，不管你怎么称呼它，人类的行为正在使地球变暖，并将带来严重的后果。

examination_example.sentence: But despite the sticky situation, firefighters and police attending to the cleanup were reportedly cheerful about the long task <highlight>ahead</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽管形势严峻，但据报道，参与清理工作的消防员和警察对未来的漫长任务感到高兴。

sense_info_list.zh: (get ahead)取得进展; 获得成功

examination_example.sentence: If you weren't changing companies every three or four years, you simply weren't getting <highlight>ahead</highlight> in your career.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你不是每三、四年换一家公司，你的职业生涯就根本没有在进步。

examination_example.sentence: According to some people living in San Jose, it has become much harder for the poor get <highlight>ahead</highlight> due to the increased inequality.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 据一些住在圣何塞的人说，由于不平等加剧，穷人想要出人头地变得更加困难。

examination_example.sentence: When they look <highlight>ahead</highlight>, they see roadblocks to their success.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当她们展望未来时，却发现通往成功的路上满是荆棘。

sense_info_list.en: higher in number; amount; or value than previously

examination_example.sentence: Others in the US have found similar effects with National Institutes of Health early-career fellowships launching narrow winners far <highlight>ahead</highlight> of close losers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国的其他人也发现了类似的效应，即美国国立卫生研究院的早期职业研究项目中，小赢家远远领先于小输家。

examination_example.sentence: You just have to do a little thinking <highlight>ahead</highlight> and redefine what qualifies as dinner.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你只需要提前想一下，重新定义什么是晚餐。

examination_example.sentence: Surprisingly, the Space Roaster concept—should it go <highlight>ahead</highlight>—will not be the first attempt to take coffee into space.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 令人惊讶的是，太空烘焙机的概念——如果可以实现的话——将不是第一次尝试将咖啡带入太空。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: I couldn't see what was <highlight>ahead</highlight> of me.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我看不到前方有什么。

examination_example.sentence: I saw a man under a tree up <highlight>ahead</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我看见前面一棵树下有一个人。

examination_example.sentence: Go straight <highlight>ahead</highlight>; you can't miss it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一直往前走；你不会错过的。

examination_example.sentence: Before we went <highlight>ahead</highlight> and dug up the grass, we spent some time thinking about where it would work best.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在我们进行挖草之前，我们花了一些时间考虑哪里最好。

examination_example.sentence: Hope the following suggestions can help to ignore those ideas and go <highlight>ahead</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 希望以下建议可以帮助忽略那些想法，继续进行。

sense_info_list.zh: 提前; 预先; 提早

examination_example.sentence: Making a list of things <highlight>ahead</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 提前列出事情的列表。

examination_example.sentence: Soon they may be able to forecast the weather for more than two weeks or more <highlight>ahead</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 很快他们就能提前预测未来两周或更长时间的天气。

examination_example.sentence: So if you are in the city, be sure to check the schedule of the events <highlight>ahead</highlight> of time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 所以如果你在这个城市，一定要提前查看活动日程。

examination_example.sentence: Tonga is <highlight>ahead</highlight> of the rest of the world: it's the first country in the world to start a new day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 汤加领先于世界其他国家:它是世界上第一个开始新一天的国家。

examination_example.sentence: With the rapid development, China is staying <highlight>ahead</highlight> in many fields and is playing its role in the world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 随着快速发展，中国在许多领域保持领先，并在世界上发挥着自己的作用。

examination_example.sentence: America is far <highlight>ahead</highlight> of other countries in space research.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国在太空研究方面遥遥领先于其他国家。
